                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4207" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0651</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8568 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内联升三里屯再玩“快闪”，老字号时尚化转型新征程？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Time-honored Brand Neiliansheng：Again Plays &quot; Pop-up Shop&quot; in BeiJing Sanlitun---the New Journey of Fashion Strategic Transformation?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张景云，吕欣欣，康泽彪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张景云</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吕欣欣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京内联升鞋业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">快闪店；品牌体验；品牌传播；新零售；老字号品牌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Pop-up Shop；Brand Experience；Brand Communication；New Retail; Time-honored Brand</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例主要描述了2018年8月10日-19日期间内联升三里屯快闪店“民国潮牌1918-2018”项目开展的情况。此次活动依托三里屯10周年潮鞋季主题活动开展，通过“快闪店”这一新零售形式，将内联升带出传统商业街，走进时尚潮流街，为参观人士带来全新的体验。本案例旨在启发学生理解“快闪店”这一新零售营销模式，掌握“快闪店”区域布局、主要功能、运作模式以及品牌体验和品牌传播等知识点，有助于《零售管理》和《品牌管理》相关知识点的教学，促进学生对老字号“新零售”模式及老字号品牌体验等问题的深入思考，提升创新决策能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case mainly describes the implementation of the project, &quot; Republican fashion brand 1918-2018&quot; in BeiJing Sanlitun Pop-up Shop, from August 10 to 19, 2018. Relying on the theme activities---the 10th anniversary shoe season in Sanlitun, the new retail form of &quot;Flash Shop&quot; event takes Neiliansheng out of the traditional commercial street and steps into the fashion trend street. Sanlitun, located at 19 Sanlitun Road, Chaoyang District, BeiJing is the symbol of the fashion trend. In this place Neiliansheng brings new experience to customers in the form of flash. The purpose of this case is to inspire students to understand the creative marketing mode of &quot; Pop-up Shop &quot;, and then to grasp the knowledge points of &quot; Pop-up Shop &quot; such as regional layout, main functions, operation mode, brand experience and brand communication. It contributes to the teaching of retail management and brand management, to drive students to think deeply about the new retail model and brand experience of Time-honored brands, and to enhance their innovative decision-making ability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》、《零售管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌生命周期、品牌传播、品牌体验、零售店布局、新零售</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-11</td>
                            </tr>
